# Preferences

How I want to work with AI assistants. This is the first file the agent
reads at the start of every session.

## Communication style

- Concise — short responses, no fluff
- Honest disagreement when warranted; don't rubber-stamp my plan
- Update me at key moments, not every step

## Code style

- (project-specific; agent should defer to project conventions)
- Minimal comments — only WHY, never WHAT

## Risk tolerance

- Local edits + reversible operations: proceed without asking
- Push, force-push, deploy, delete: confirm explicitly
- Money, prod data, user-visible changes: confirm explicitly
